argin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(205, 80, 41); width: 30px; height: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">0</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1</strong></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 10px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 15.969 23" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #fffffe;stroke: #cd5029;stroke-width: 1px;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M386.369,11319l-14.383-11,14.383-11" transform="translate(-371.5 -11296.5)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -3px; padding: 3px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(202, 69, 28); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(205, 80, 41);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">C220518陈美灵</strong></section></section></section><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">毛泽东一生矢志不渝地为中国人民的利益而奋斗，他在中国历史上留下了独特的印记。他的成长之路是一段艰辛而壮丽的历程，他的领导智慧和英勇决策成就了他伟大的领袖地位。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">毛泽东是中国历史上不可磨灭的名字，他的故事激励着世代的青年奋发向前。他的成长经历告诉我们，作为一名新时代青年要有坚定的信念和不屈不挠的奋斗精神。在纪念毛泽东的同时，我们也要思考他留给我们的宝贵精神财富：对知识的渴望永不止步，为民族和国家的利益奋斗不息。正是因为他的努力和奉献，中国得以崛起，并在世界舞台上扮演着越来越重要的角色。</span></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(205, 80, 41); width: 30px; height: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">0</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2</strong></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 10px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 15.969 23" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #fffffe;stroke: #cd5029;stroke-width: 1px;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M386.369,11319l-14.383-11,14.383-11" transform="translate(-371.5 -11296.5)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -3px; padding: 3px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(202, 69, 28); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(205, 80, 41);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">B210506乐一扬</strong></section></section></section><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">12月26日是伟人毛泽东的诞辰。他是革命家，是战士，是诗人，是领袖。他虽然已经离开我们40多年了，但无论是过去，现在还是将来，他的名字，他的思想，他的风范，都深刻地影响和教育着一代又一代人。毛泽东曾说过，中国人民有志气，有能力，一定要在不远的将来赶上和超过世界先进水平。今天的我们，正站在两个一百年奋斗目标的历史交汇点，见证了伟大祖国日新月异的发展，今日强大的中国正如伟人所愿。“俱往矣，数风流人物，还看今朝。”让我们用行动弘扬毛泽东思想的伟大精神，争做新时代好青年，向着中华民族伟大复兴中国梦奋勇前进。</span></p></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(205, 80, 41); width: 30px; height: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">0</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3</strong></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; z-index: 9;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 10px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 15.969 23" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #fffffe;stroke: #cd5029;stroke-width: 1px;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M386.369,11319l-14.383-11,14.383-11" transform="translate(-371.5 -11296.5)"></path></svg></section></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -3px; padding: 3px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(202, 69, 28); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(205, 80, 41);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">B220503刘琳</strong></section></section></section><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">今年是毛泽东诞辰130周年，虽然他早已逝世，但是他仍是一座不朽的丰碑，是我们心中的太阳，永远活在每一位中国人的心中。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在此次毛主席生平事迹分享会中，让我更深入地认识毛主席。毛主席一生爱学习，好学习，勤学习，少年之时，毛主席写下“孤儿立志出乡关，学不成名誓不还”，而在那个以革命救亡图存的时代，毛主席不仅仅只是单纯的学，而是将理论知识系统地运用到实际当中，推动着中国革命事业的发展。他引领中国革命事业前进，不仅伟大，而且还谦虚，始终保持艰苦奋斗的作风。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">毛主席意气风发，抱负远大，独立自强，一直在激励着我们奋勇前行，就像那“星星之火”，却可以“燎原”，新时代的我们，要以青年之力，共创辉煌。</span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/><br/></p><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: auto; min-width: 5%; flex: 0 0 auto; height: auto; align-self: flex-end;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; width: 32.85px; flex-flow: column;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; z-index: 1;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; line-height: 0;"><br/></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center; justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 18px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 657px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); height: auto; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(219, 95, 54); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.6;"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="132766" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px -10px -12px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 30px;"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(236, 52, 33); display: flex; flex-direction: column;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 20px 3px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; z-index: 9;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">总结</strong></p></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: -10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 74px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 256.2 30.8" style="display: block;"><g data-name="图层 2"><g data-name="图层 1"><path style="fill:#f9e189;" d="M0,.86V13.32C34.25,24.22,78.59,30.8,127,30.8c49.45,0,94.63-6.85,129.16-18.16V0C221.67,14.25,176.49,23.8,127,23.8,78.59,23.8,34.25,14.63,0,.86Z"></path></g></g></svg></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.14285em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">毛主席的一生都在为祖国、为人民做贡献。祖国和人民永远不会忘记是毛主席改变了中国的命运，让亿万中国人站了起来。本次分享会让大家了解并学习到毛主席的生平事迹，毛主席的精神激励着入党积极分子们为中国的宏伟蓝图建设贡献一份自己的力量，永远鼓舞着我们新时代青年为中华民族的伟大梦想努力奋进。</span></p></section></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>